<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact Frost & Scoop Co. Ice Cream Shop Right Now </title>
  <meta name="description" content="Contact Frost & Scoop Co. – your premium icecream shop. Reach us for organic ice cream, delicious icecream flavors, or any questions. We'd love to hear from you!">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #0d0b0a;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      line-height: 1.5;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, .logo, .nav-links a, .page-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }

    .container { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 999;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(13, 11, 10, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e8e0d8; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .logo i { color: #d4af37; margin-right: 6px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.2rem; font-weight: 500; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #c8c0b8;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { border-bottom-color: #d4af37; color: #d4af37; }

    /* ===== CONTACT HERO ===== */
    .contact-hero {
      padding: 6rem 2rem 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0d0b0a 0%, #1a1512 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .contact-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.04) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 70%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .contact-hero .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      color: #d4af37;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .page-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 4.2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease-out 0.1s forwards;
    }
    .page-title span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #f0d060, #d4af37);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: goldShine 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes goldShine { 0%,100%{background-position:0% 50%;} 50%{background-position:100% 50%;} }
    .contact-hero p {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 1rem auto 0;
      color: #a89888;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp { 0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);} 100%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);} }

    /* ===== QUICK INFO CARDS ===== */
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.4rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    .info-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.6rem;
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      border-radius: 1.8rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.09);
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .info-card:hover {
      background: rgba(30, 25, 22, 0.9);
      border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
      transform: translateY(-6px);
    }
    .info-card i {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #d4af37;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .info-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .info-card p, .info-card a {
      color: #a89888;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
    }
    .info-card a:hover { color: #d4af37; }

    /* ===== CONTACT MAIN: FORM + MAP ===== */
    .contact-main {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .form-panel {
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.09);
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }
    .form-panel h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .form-panel .section-note-inline {
      color: #8a7a6a;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
    .form-group label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #a89888;
    }
    .form-group input,
    .form-group select,
    .form-group textarea {
      padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      background: rgba(13, 11, 10, 0.6);
      color: #e8e0d8;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }
    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group select:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #d4af37;
      background: rgba(13, 11, 10, 0.9);
    }
    .form-group input::placeholder, .form-group textarea::placeholder { color: #5a4a3a; }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.4rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #b8941e);
      color: #0d0b0a;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px -8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px -8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0c040, #d4af37);
    }
    .btn-block { width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: 0.4rem; }

    .form-success {
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
      color: #d4af37;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .form-success.show { display: flex; }

    /* Side panel: map + hours */
    .side-panel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.4rem; }

    .map-card {
      border-radius: 2rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.09);
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      position: relative;
      min-height: 260px;
    }
    .map-card iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 260px;
      border: 0;
      display: block;
      filter: grayscale(0.3) contrast(1.05);
    }

    .hours-card {
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.09);
      padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
    }
    .hours-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }
    .hours-card h3 i { color: #d4af37; }
    .hours-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .hours-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .hours-row span:first-child { color: #c8c0b8; }
    .hours-row span:last-child { color: #a89888; font-weight: 300; }
    .hours-row.today span:first-child { color: #d4af37; font-weight: 600; }

    .social-card {
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.09);
      padding: 1.6rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .social-card p { color: #a89888; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 300; }
    .social-card .social i {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-left: 1rem;
      color: #8a7a6a;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }
    .social-card .social i:hover { color: #d4af37; transform: scale(1.1); }

    /* ===== FAQ ===== */
    .faq-section { margin: 1rem 0 4rem; }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      left: 0;
      width: 50px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d4af37, transparent);
    }
    .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem; }
    .faq-item {
      background: rgba(20, 17, 15, 0.6);
      border-radius: 1.4rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .faq-item summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.6rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-item summary i { color: #d4af37; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .faq-item[open] summary i { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .faq-item p {
      padding: 0 1.6rem 1.3rem;
      color: #8a7a6a;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .footer-links a { margin: 0 1rem 0 0; color: #8a7a6a; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s ease; font-weight: 300; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: #d4af37; }
    .footer-links span { color: #4a3a2a; }
    .social i { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-left: 1rem; color: #5a4a3a; transition: 0.3s ease; }
    .social i:hover { color: #d4af37; transform: scale(1.1); }

    .back-to-top {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 2rem;
      right: 2rem;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      padding: 0.8rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      color: #d4af37;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .back-to-top:hover {
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
      transform: scale(1.05);
      color: #f0d060;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .contact-main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .nav-links { gap: 1rem; }
      .container { padding: 0 1.2rem; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .form-panel { padding: 1.8rem 1.4rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo"><i class="fas fa-ice-cream"></i> Frost & Scoop</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
    <a href="menu-ice-cream-shop.html">Menu</a>
    <a href="contactus-ice-cream-shop.html" class="active">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="contact-hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">We'd love to hear from you</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Get in <span>Touch</span></h1>
  <p>Questions about flavors, catering, or a big scoop of feedback? Send us a note or stop by the shop — either way, we're listening.</p>
</section>

<main class="container">

  <!-- QUICK INFO -->
  <div class="info-grid">
    <div class="info-card">
      <i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i>
      <h3>Visit Us</h3>
      <p>124 Maple Grove Lane<br>Riverside District</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
      <h3>Call Us</h3>
      <a href="tel:+15551234567">(555) 123-4567</a>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
      <h3>Email Us</h3>
      <a href="mailto:hello@frostandscoop.com">hello@frostandscoop.com</a>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
      <h3>Open Today</h3>
      <p>11:00 AM – 9:00 PM</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FORM + MAP -->
  <div class="contact-main">
    <div class="form-panel">
      <h2>Send Us a Message</h2>
      <p class="section-note-inline">We typically reply within one business day.</p>
      <form id="contact-form">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="firstName">First Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" placeholder="Emma" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="lastName">Last Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" placeholder="Carter" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="(555) 000-0000">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="topic">What's this about?</label>
          <select id="topic">
            <option>General question</option>
            <option>Catering & events</option>
            <option>Flavor suggestion</option>
            <option>Feedback</option>
            <option>Careers</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind..." required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block">Send Message</button>
        <div class="form-success" id="form-success">
          <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Thanks! Your message is on its way to us.
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="side-panel">
      <div class="map-card">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=New+York,+NY&output=embed"
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="Frost & Scoop location map">
        </iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="hours-card">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Store Hours</h3>
        <div class="hours-row today"><span>Today</span><span>11:00 AM – 9:00 PM</span></div>
        <div class="hours-row"><span>Mon – Thu</span><span>11:00 AM – 9:00 PM</span></div>
        <div class="hours-row"><span>Fri – Sat</span><span>11:00 AM – 10:30 PM</span></div>
        <div class="hours-row"><span>Sunday</span><span>12:00 PM – 8:00 PM</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="social-card">
        <p>Follow the scoop</p>
        <div class="social">
          <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you cater private events? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></summary>
        <p>Yes — we cater birthdays, weddings, and corporate events with scoop bars, pre-packed cups, or a full sundae station. Share your headcount and date in the form above and we'll follow up with options.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are any flavors dairy-free or vegan? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></summary>
        <p>We currently rotate one or two plant-based flavors seasonally. Ask our staff in-shop or mention it in your message and we'll let you know what's available this week.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I place a large pickup order in advance? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></summary>
        <p>Absolutely. Orders of a half-gallon or more are best placed at least 24 hours ahead so we can pack everything fresh for your pickup time.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you have gluten-free options? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></summary>
        <p>Several of our scoops are gluten-free — check the tags on our menu page, or ask a team member for the current list, since seasonal flavors vary.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<footer class="container">
  <div class="footer-links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a> <a href="menu-ice-cream-shop.html">Menu</a> <a href="contactus-ice-cream-shop.html">Contact</a> <span>© 2026 Frost & Scoop</span>
  </div>
  <div class="social">
    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
    <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
    <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
  </div>
</footer>

<a href="#" class="back-to-top"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></a>

<script>
  document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    document.getElementById('form-success').classList.add('show');
    this.reset();
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
